,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:17:19.000Z","msg":"同時依家都每日固定有幾千人online  搵人刷副本打王都絕對夠人<br />\n<a href=\"http://steamcharts.com/app/372000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsteamcharts.com%2Fapp%2F372000&d=9ePMVzXEYMuVz5kEOTnnBW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=ff733906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://steamcharts.com/app/372000</a><br />\n<br />\n同時依家卡片全面改版<br />\n<a href=\"https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=3661825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhome.gamer.com.tw%2FcreationDetail.php%3Fsn%3D3661825&d=9ePMVzXEYMuVz5kEOTnnBW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=d5c09acd\" target=\"_blank\">https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=3661825</a><br />\n<br />\n好多新野出左"},{"pid":"4e86bf1fbbc3349d556c54650a61f4482778bf9d","tid":417450,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:56:15.000Z","msg":"唔出R9 玩撚咩 我個神論差1個轉職位呀 DLLM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134351d02f8dffedf82c5b06e363472d06af9f52","tid":417450,"uid":37267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T17:23:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔出R9 玩撚咩 我個神論差1個轉職位呀 DLLM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢依家set左做R8係最終職  同埋之前既R7職會加上C3技  R8職就加C2技<br />\n新既職業係R8黎 有C1+C2 技"},{"pid":"d619d8216774b9dc365695685abd0acfc2d6e2c9","tid":417450,"uid":37267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T17:32:55.000Z","msg":"以下為轉載<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/TreeofSavior/M.1506599844.A.66E.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FTreeofSavior%2FM.1506599844.A.66E.html&d=9ePMVzXEYMuVz5kEOTnnBW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=c10a70c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/TreeofSavior/M.1506599844.A.66E.html</a><br />\n<br />\n沒有R9！！<br />\n<br />\n應該說，沒有R9職。<br />\n<br />\nR8將會是救世者之樹這款遊戲（以職業來說）的最高rank。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然而，近期將會實裝四個新職業（四職業系各一個），<br />\n<br />\n而且這四個職業會位於R8，<br />\n<br />\n也就是各職業別的R8，將會總共有三種職業可以選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除了新職業外，<br />\n<br />\nR7職將會新增C3技能、R8職也將會新增C2技能；<br />\n<br />\n此次登場的四種R8新職業，也會同時實裝兩個circle的技能。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/OKL0Lj7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FOKL0Lj7.gif&h=34b87bec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲重砲手的C3新技能<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n並且，<br />\n<br />\n往後的新職業，<br />\n<br />\n將會變更為各職業別一個一個依序的方式來出現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/SjqAzN5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FSjqAzN5.png&h=4fa751ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲新rank系統示意圖，往後仍會持續向更高的rank擴張<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，<br />\n<br />\n官方團隊往後也預計在低階的職業上新增「大師circle」，<br />\n<br />\n可將技能的能力提升至高階的水準，（感覺可能類似C4之類的）<br />\n<br />\n然目前未釋出太多細節。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二、轉職方式變更<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此次所新增的新R8職業，<br />\n<br />\n必須達成一定的解鎖條件，與導師對話後，方可轉職。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/lCZjEgD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FlCZjEgD.png&h=9d40eb86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲新R8法師系職業「幻影法師」轉職中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既存的職業，<br />\n<br />\n在轉職的職業選單中選擇後，<br />\n<br />\n即可立即轉職，不須再解轉職任務。<br />\n<br />\n舊有的轉職任務，<br />\n<br />\n將改編為獨立型支線任務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，<br />\n<br />\n此次新增的四種R8新職業，<br />\n<br />\n轉職過後，可再向導師承接專屬特殊任務。<br />\n<br />\n完成後，依照任務的難易度，<br />\n<br />\n可獲得該職業的專屬特殊時裝或裝飾品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/1EfNQbp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F1EfNQbp.png&h=ef673117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲新R8牧師系職業「狂熱者」的四種時裝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三、職業重返系統<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單說就是可以將角色往回一個rank的功能。<br />\n<br />\n然而只能返回一次，<br />\n<br />\n並且會遺失該rank的職業等級經驗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前官方尚未釋出新職業與新技能的詳細情報。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然而，有一張新四職的剪影圖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/LJuqRSf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FLJuqRSf.png&h=3d3ff0d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前已知：<br />\n<br />\n左一為法師系的「幻影法師 Shadowmancer」；<br />\n<br />\n右二為牧師系的「狂熱者 Zealot」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於左二，可能為劍士系的「鬥牛士 Matador」；<br />\n<br />\n而，右二，職業不明，<br />\n<br />\n但看起來似乎會是拿雙鎗的弓箭手職？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果真的是的話，另外兩個已知的未實裝弓職，玩偶師、吹笛手，<br />\n<br />\n又得繼續躺在客戶端裏頭了。"},{"pid":"db03870556f5e9170b67fc45bc4902e217e7f0ba","tid":417450,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T18:05:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔出R9 玩撚咩 我個神論差1個轉職位呀 DLLM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢依家set左做R8係最終職  同埋之前既R7職會加上C3技  R8職就加C2技<br />\n新既職業係R8黎 有C1+C2 技</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁佢就CUT左C3佢啦 那有位"},{"pid":"d9a02caf5e30542847ad62d1ceada95f80cc8ab9","tid":417450,"uid":49703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T18:07:57.000Z","msg":"法元咒 感覺玩唔到落去之後就棄左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0223ea0612763017338120d4cd39aed273b1f0bf","tid":417450,"uid":37267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T19:07:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔出